```suggestion
* `MemHolder r f`: Predicate for a function `f` being `r`-Hölder continuous.

```

```suggestion
`r`-Hölder constant. This is equivalent to `f` having finite Hölder norm.
```

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Germanic_umlaut#Substitution says Hölder should be transcribed to Hoelder in ASCII
```suggestion

lemma eHoelderNorm_nsmul [Module ℝ Y] [BoundedSMul ℝ Y] (c : ℝ) :

lemma eHoelderNorm_nsmul [Module ℝ Y] [BoundedSMul ℝ Y] (n : ℕ) :

```
